javax.accessibility.Accessible, GenericToolBarTarget, HTMLQueryResultHandler, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, QueryResultDisplay, java.io.Serializable
public class SkycatCatalogNavigator
extends CatalogNavigator

Used to navigate the catalog hierarchy. It displays a tree of catalogs in one panel and the interface for searching the catalog, or the query results in the other panel.

The tree display is based on a given top level catalog config file. One such starting point would be http://archive.eso.org/skycat/skycat2.0.cfg. This file contains links to various catalogs and image servers as well as other catalog config files (or catalog directories).
